  ShortDesc: BLADE - PHYS - DEX - ALC
  LongDesc: 'These brave warriors are a disorderly bunch- thrown together to form
    an army from different backgrounds, loose training routines, and a hatred for
    hierarchy. But their differences make the Coalition military strong and determined
    to prove the world otherwise. With good survival skills forged in their harsh
    environments, these versatile warriors stand ready to fight.


    STARTING ITEMS:
    BLADE

    PHYS +2

    DEX +1

    ALC +1'
